title: Blood Moon Elise

embed.description: Full animated 3D models for LoL champion Blood Moon Elise, try all of the skins!

body:
I thought it was a twisted version of a HeartSeeker skin. 
It just doesn't fit in to the BloodMoon skins. Just compare it to the BloodMoon Thresh
By all means, I like the skin but I just think it could be better imo.
